---

<ApplicationLayout
  title="Explosion Proof Centrifuge | Hazardous Area Certified"
  pageTitle="Explosion Proof Centrifuge | Hazardous Location Centrifuge"
  description="An explosion proof centrifuge is suitable for operating in hazardous areas in the presence of flammable material on offshore Oil &amp; Gas platforms."
